 &HT;    
 &HT;    A5316 BC-PAKISTAN-BUS-ART-535&AMP;ADD-NYT 1000 19:18 U I
 &HT;    JUST BUS RIDERS, CAUGHT UP IN SHUTTLE DIPLOMACY
 &HT;    
 &HT;    A5312 BC-ALBANIA-VOLUNTEERS-BOS 797 19:16 U I
 &HT;    VOLUNTEERS TRAIN, MOVE OUT IN SUPPORT OF KLA
 &HT;    
 &HT;    A5305 BC-KOSOVO-TRAIN-990(2TAKES)-NYT 1043 19:09 U I
 &HT;    NATO PLANES HIT BRIDGE IN SERBIA, KILLING 9 ON TRAIN
 &HT;    
 &HT;    A5306 BC-KOSOVO-TRAIN-2TAKES-NYT 579 19:09 U I
 &HT;    GRDELICA: that Snoopy.''
 &HT;    
 &HT;    A5269 BC-ELIMINATE-CHINA-NUKELAB-NYT 33 18:41 U I
 &HT;    
 &HT;    
 &HT;    A5248 BC-RUSSIA-POLITICS-NYT 622 18:22 U I
 &HT;    IMPEACHMENT VOTE ON YELTSIN POSTPONED
 &HT;    
 &HT;    A5247 BC-SPOT-BUDGET-BOS 421 18:21 U I
