   NATIONAL NEWS (``a'' category)
</P>
<P>
   READ (Houston) _ The Houston READ Commission, formed in 1988,
has grown into the largest urban literacy coalition in the United
States, one copied throughout the nation. By MELISSA FLETCHER
STOELTJE.
</P>
<P>
   IRS-DUMMY (San Francisco) _ When a dummy takes on the Internal
Revenue Service, well, you can guess the outcome. The dummy takes
