   CHECKFREE _ ATLANTA _We have a copy of the lawsuit filed by
Intuit against CheckFree. the complaint seems to say the CheckFree
did sign a deal with Yahoo!, which we've reported but they have not
announced. Talking to an analyst who thinks the complaint is a
``win-win'' for CheckFree. (Clothier, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
