<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-FRONTPAGE-1STLD-WRITETHRU-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
(HLW)
</HEADLINE>
  
(SUBS to add CHINA-TRADE; COUNSEL-LAW is now on fold, with EPA-SUV;
KOSOVO-CONGRESS is inside; KOSOVO-MACEDONIA is now on bottom of
page)
<TEXT>
<P>
   Here are the stories that New York Times editors are planning
